YouTube Just another incredibly beautiful acoustic guitar performance by Tommy Emmanuel, that’s all. This song was written by Martin Taylor for his late son Stewart, who sadly passed at the age of 21. [Subscribe] goo.gl [Like] facebook.com [Follow] twitter.com [Official Web Site] tommyemmanuel.com
